?                 The options arise from the taxonomy of Anderson and Krathwohl. The options describe the relevant cognitive process underlying the achievement of a learning objective. The options are hierarchically and every step contains the previous dimensions.
                    Remember: The students can remember relevant knowledge from their long-term memory.
